                      1. Switch on |entry|[1]:

                      : {{File}}
                      :: [=list/Append=] a new {{UploadData}} with
                          {{UploadData/file}} equal to |entry|[1]'s
                          {{File/name}} to |requestBody|'s
                          {{RequestBody/raw}}.

                      : {{USVString}}
                      ::  1. If |formData|[|entry|[0]] does not exist, then
                              set |formData|[|entry|[0]] equal to an empty
                              [=list=].

                          1. [=list/Append=] |entry|[1] to
                              |formData|[|entry|[0]].


